      <title>AT&T 称新黑客攻击包括客户通话和短信记录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/at-t-says-new-hack-includes-records-of-customer-calls-texts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[AT&amp;T 公司遭受了大规模客户数据黑客攻击 — — 除了今年早些时候报道的一次攻击之外 — — 这次攻击包括 2022 年六个月内几乎所有手机用户的通话和短信记录，这是近年来最大的私人通信数据泄露事件之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/at-t-says-new-hack-includes-records-of-customer-calls-texts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 10:26:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克的特斯拉 X 因对有害内容做出虚假“Blue Check”保证而遭欧盟严厉批评</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/musk-s-x-slammed-by-eu-for-its-deceptive-blue-check-assurances-on-content</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克的社交媒体平台 X 因欺骗用户参与潜在有害内容而受到欧盟的警告，这是布鲁塞尔针对大型科技公司行为的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/musk-s-x-slammed-by-eu-for-its-deceptive-blue-check-assurances-on-content</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Northern Data 预计云计算业务销售额将增长三倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/northern-data-forecasts-sales-to-triple-on-cloud-computing-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最大的加密挖矿公司之一 Northern Data AG 预测，随着其在高性能计算领域的扩张，今年的收入可能会增长两倍以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/northern-data-forecasts-sales-to-triple-on-cloud-computing-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称，Business Insider 老板 Axel Springer 正在考虑分拆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/business-insider-owner-axel-springer-is-said-to-weigh-split</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，拥有 Politico 和 Business Insider 的德国集团 Axel Springer SE 的所有者正在讨论将该公司的媒体资产与其他业务拆分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/business-insider-owner-axel-springer-is-said-to-weigh-split</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 08:15:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞银因担忧反弹而下调特斯拉评级，股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/tesla-downgraded-by-ubs-on-concern-over-ai-driven-share-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司股价下跌，此前瑞银集团下调了其股票评级，理由是人们担心这家电动汽车制造商的股价因对其人工智能计划的乐观情绪而“上涨过多、过快”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/tesla-downgraded-by-ubs-on-concern-over-ai-driven-share-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 07:31:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>三星联合工会瞄准最高端的 AI 芯片工厂，引发罢工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/samsung-union-targets-highest-end-ai-chip-plants-as-strike-flags</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三星电子公司最大的工会目前正在呼吁该公司最先进的人工智能存储芯片工厂之一的员工罢工，在争取加薪的运动出现失去动力的迹象后，工会改变了策略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/samsung-union-targets-highest-end-ai-chip-plants-as-strike-flags</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 05:23:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱立信在严峻的市场环境下削减成本，业绩超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/ericsson-earnings-beat-estimates-on-cost-cutting-in-tough-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受成本削减措施推动，爱立信第二季度盈利超出分析师预期，该公司被这家瑞典公司称为“充满挑战的市场环境”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/ericsson-earnings-beat-estimates-on-cost-cutting-in-tough-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 05:12:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾水务公司计划在蓝色债券发行后于 2025 年进行 IPO</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/philippines-first-public-blue-bond-seller-tops-off-2024-funding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[梅尼拉德水务服务公司首席执行官表示，该公司计划最早于明年进行首次股票出售，此前该公司本月通过公开发行蓝色债券筹集了 150 亿比索（2.57 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/philippines-first-public-blue-bond-seller-tops-off-2024-funding</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 04:02:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
